title: Bug 116609[Regression] Color orange doesn't work.
description: Bug 116609[Regression] Color orange doesn't work. Description: Color orange is not being displayed correctly. Steps to reproduce: 1. Apply the orange color to any element. SR: 1. Apply the orange color to any element and observe the result.
